Package com.bytedesk.ai

@NonNullApi package com.bytedesk.ai
ByteDesk AI module root package. This module provides AI-powered features for customer service, including: - Robot/Agent management - AI service provider integrations - Natural language processing - Knowledge base management - Conversation analysis
Author:
bytedesk.com
